# Implementation Plan - Vite Build Optimization

## Goal
Resolve Vite/Rollup warnings about large chunks (>500 kB) by implementing manual chunk splitting and fine-tuning build configurations.

## Proposed Changes

### [Root] [vite.config.ts](file:///c:/Users/dgper/Proyectos/ZeroCode/vite.config.ts)
- Implement `build.rollupOptions.output.manualChunks` to separate large vendor libraries (e.g., `react-router-dom`, `framer-motion`, `lucide-react`).
- Increase `chunkSizeWarningLimit` to 1000 kB.
- Ensure `minify` is set to `terser` or `esbuild` (default) for optimal compression.

## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- Run `npm run build` from the root and verify that chunk size warnings are resolved or minimized.
- Inspect the `dist` folder to ensure chunks are distributed effectively.
